      "recording_attendee_id": "43345a44-49c1-410f-9b0f-9cd7ae063bcd",
      "order_number": 6,
      "text": "But how can I help you."
    },
    {
      "id": "0b6d2331-72e7-40d7-bd5a-0087b4de4f14",
      "recording_id": "3bae7d6d-de8f-44f6-9908-d66d914a57c2",
      "end_time": 41.93,
      "start_time": 26.72,
      "recording_attendee_id": "571e78fa-d0b2-4583-b4cb-e5e85c522a0e",
      "order_number": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, so I was actually just calling this is sales call the super easy one because you can't buy anything from me. I actually was just reaching out to see kind of what occupancy was looking like um, as well as kind of how you go about market surveys. If that's even something you handle."
