      "end_time": 55.91,
      "start_time": 43.64,
      "recording_attendee_id": "43345a44-49c1-410f-9b0f-9cd7ae063bcd",
      "order_number": 8,
      "text": "I usually yeah, the market surveys I usually call the other properties around the area and I get the output from them just when needed and the occupancy we are a hundred percent."
