      "recording_attendee_id": "571e78fa-d0b2-4583-b4cb-e5e85c522a0e",
      "order_number": 9,
      "text": "Let's see okay. Yeah, I kinda figured that would be the case with occupancy. Um, I guess is that kind of the same was probably the sixty day projections then."
