      "recording_attendee_id": "43345a44-49c1-410f-9b0f-9cd7ae063bcd",
      "order_number": 10,
      "text": "Yes, um, I mean for me as a thank God. For this um, I don't have that much rotation on my residence on this there's a Hurricane or another close in the area."
    },
