      "recording_attendee_id": "571e78fa-d0b2-4583-b4cb-e5e85c522a0e",
      "order_number": 11,
      "text": "Yeah. Okay, good, yeah, well, I'm glad for you. Then, yeah, that's awesome. I'm sure that"
